<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.3.10">
<l>tōṭuviṇṭa larpūmpo ḻilmaṅkai yartōṉṟal vāḷkali yaṉtiru vāli</l>
<l>nāṭaṉaṉṉa ṟaiyūrniṉ ṟanampi taṉnalla māmalar cēvaṭi ceṉṉiyil</l>
<l>cūṭiyumto ḻutume ḻuntāṭi yuntoṇṭar kaṭkavaṉ coṉṉacol mālai</l>
<l>pāṭalpatti vaipāṭu miṉtoṇṭīr pāṭa nummiṭaip pāvanil lāvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devotees, sing these ten songs of the garland of verse</l>
<l rend="indent">he composed for devotees, the one of Tiruvāli lands,</l>
<l>Sword[-wielding] Kaliyaṉ, the ruler of those of Maṅkai,</l>
<l rend="indent">its flowering gardens with petal-spread blossoms,</l>
<l>Adorning your heads with the beautiful, fine, flower[-like] rosy feet</l>
<l rend="indent">of the noble who stands in good Naṟaiyūr,</l>
<l>Adoring [him], leaping and dancing! If you sing,</l>
<l rend="indent">misfortune will not stay with you.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
